Okhulumela abakwa-ER24, uMnuz Ross Campbell, uthe bafike endaweni yesehlo sekukhona abezinye izinkampani zabezimo eziphuthumayo bathola abesifazane ababili nomlisa oyedwa belele phansi ngaphandle kwemoto. Bonke laba uthe bebelimele kanzima kanti banikwe usizo oluphuthumayo base bephuthunyiswa esibhedlela i-Edendale naseNorthdale ukuze banikwe okunye ukunakekelwa kwezempilo. Omunye umuntu wesine obekule moto kukholakala ukuthi ubalekile endaweni yesehlo. Kwenye ingozi kulimale abantu abayisikhombisa ngesikhathi kugingqika imoto emgwaqweni uN3 phakathi kwaseHowick naseMooi River izolo ekuseni. UCampbell uthe bafike nabezinye izinkampani zabezimo eziphuthumayo ngabo 9 ekuseni bafica abantu belele phansi eceleni komgwaqo. Uveze ukuthi imoto i-Toyota Avanza ishayisile yaze yayoma kwenye ingxenye yomgwaqo. Uthe bonke abalimele okungabantu abadala kanti abanye balimele okungatheni. Abalimele baphuthunyiswe esibhedlela iNorthdale, Greys nase-Edendale.